				<td colspan="2"><span>Even before your last response, my evaluation was that it would definitely be worth it, but it would be taxing -- for all the reasons you mentioned.  If you absolutely HAVE to have high DPS for a reasonably short period of time, it's a great idea.  Obviously, there are limits to how long you could use this tactic without it burning you out or having everything go wrong at once and wipe you, but still, I think it is a very viable option for fighting in HOH.</span></td>
