			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Another reason it works in HoH is just because of the zone, especially in the basements.  Unless you pull like 4 mobs, it's hard to get into too much trouble w/ selos up - there's just too much room to get out of the way, even after a stun.  In my situation add to that a pretty definite chance of having SoE up, should selos happen to drop, and you would have to mess up very baddly to get into trouble enough to wipe.  
<br />

<br />
I don't think it would be a good idea in, say, PoV, but in HoH, it's very doable.</span></td>
